      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const name = String($json['Name'] ?? $json['NAME'] ?? $json['name'] ?? '').trim();\nconst emailSubject = `Partnership Opportunity: Polish Party x ${name}`;\n\nconst greetingName = name ? `${name} ` : '';\nconst emailBody = [\n  `Hi ${greetingName}team,`,\n  '',\n  'I’m Jordie, a textile and nail artist based in LA. The way you’ve cultivated a space that centers healing, culture, and joy especially for queer and BIPOC communities feels deeply aligned with the work I do.',\n  '',\n  'I’d love to bring The Polish Party to your community, a hands-on nail art workshop where folks of all genders are invited to slow down, get creative, and design their own press-on nail sets using gel polish, charms, stickers, and more. It’s a joyful, affirming space where self-expression and play are centered. I offer a short demo, then invite guests to freestyle or pull from themed inspo cards. We close with a little gallery walk, and everyone leaves with a set they created and can carry out into the world.',\n  '',\n  \"This is a new offering but it has been a hit at Aura Creative Co in Lincoln Heights, with upcoming sessions at Nova Community Arts and Junior High LA. I provide all materials and tools, it's beginner friendly and no nail art experience needed.\",\n  '',\n  'If this feels like a good fit for your public programming, I’d love to connect and explore partnership further.',\n].join('\\n');\n\nreturn [\n  {\n    json: {\n      ...$json,\n      'Email Subject': emailSubject,\n      'Email Body': emailBody,\n    },\n  },\n];"
      },
