      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 1. Setup Guide\n*  ### Configure the timer node to your desired execution frequency.\n* ### Duplicate the provided [Google Sheet Template](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/145fry3jHIP0kxOamDTl0ROb2o9hr27wALa4Sw80t9qo/edit?usp=sharing).\n* ### Link the duplicated sheet within both the \"Get Emails\" and \"Update Record\" nodes.\n* ### Select your preferred email sending node and use the \"Limit\" node to manage the volume of emails dispatched.\n\n## 2. Help\n* ### For detailed instructions, please refer to our [Detailed Setup Guide](https://docs.google.com/document/d/1vVJW97H0rXs5RJ0EBcfdpHM39eGA88wr9yT-lDd0rr4/edit?usp=sharing).",
